text: Sarah Wilhite Parsons (born 30 July 1995) is an American volleyball player. She played at the 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, 2018 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup, 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League, 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. She played for the University of Minnesota's women's volleyball team, MTV Stuttgart 1843, and Futura Volley Busto Arsizio. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:American volleyball players
